      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for its next owner who doesn't mind a bit of character. While it runs and drives reliably, the exterior shows visible signs of its age, including several scratches, minor dings on the body panels, and some fading in the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear and staining from regular use. It is up to date on basic maintenance, though it may soon require attention to the suspension and a set of new tires. This is an honest, dependable car for someone looking for a budget-friendly option that gets the job done.",
