    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved? This beauty is ready for its next adventure! It runs like a dream and has been kept in really nice shape over the years. It's perfect for weekend road trips or just zipping around town\u2014you're going to love how smooth it handles. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
