    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone essential preventive maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate chassis fatigue. Power is transmitted through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the engine maintains strong compression across all cylinders. While the aesthetic condition shows minor patina consistent with its 'good' rating, the drivetrain and longitudinal dynamics remain sharp and responsive for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Well-maintained vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Routine service records available. Minor cosmetic wear on exterior. Engine runs smooth. Interior is clean.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
