    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between luxury and practical performance. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, showing only the slight, expected character marks of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, non-smoking cabin where the premium upholstery remains firm and comfortable, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, this car has been treated to a rigorous maintenance schedule; we recently completed a full fluid flush and a multi-point inspection to ensure it remains turn-key ready for its next owner. The engine delivers smooth, responsive power, while the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a documented service history. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
      "price": 34500.0,
