    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, reliable drive without any fuss. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more miles on the road. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have, so come take a look and see for yourself!",
